data.description: Magnificent Ranch home built in 2021, no HOA.  The home features open floor plan, with huge living room area, and dining room, with a nice den. The huge kitchen has an open floor plan with an island for great entertainment. The property has 4 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms with a  2-Car Garage. The home is built on a quarter lot, with a nice size screened patio in the back with, pavers in the front of the home and surrounding the home. The roof has upgraded gutters. In all a beautiful home to raise a family. The home is located east of the Turnpike and fairly close to the beach
